{"word":"προχοή","slug":"προχοή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προχοή</b></el> <el>(προχοή, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:προχέω'><el>προχέω</el></a>\n<p/>mostly in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a>, <i>the outpouring</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>the mouth</i>, of a river, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; sg. in <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/>"}]}